      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "YOUR MAJESTY (10) resumes after three months but was racing well last time in, winning the last two two times she raced here, one of those from this barrier when over this distance. Proven fresh and was readied with a trial pacing so expecting a bright start to the campaign. LEAF STRIDE NZ (9) didn't fire in two outings last prep but had good form here in the previous campaign. Usually races well when fresh and should be ready to go off three trials. ICONIC IMAGE (2) is first up for six months after tackling the good juveniles last season, last seen in the G1 Redwood Classic when he bombed the standing start. He was a G2 winner in Brisbane earlier in that prep. Now with Anton Golino and has been readied with three solid trials. Has won when fresh before and should be competitive from an ideal draw. MAXIMUS MERIDIUS (8) was midfield in a stronger race last time and came from this barrier when second here prior. Respect.",
